snippet.title: Primal Fray – Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2357350/Primal_Fray/ 
Primal Fray is a turn-based strategy roguelite. Enter the Rift and fight your way through enemies while building a team of primals and collecting buffs along the way. Outmaneuver your foes and surprise them with powerful combos of a well-built and synergistic team to learn the truth about the Rift.
